        "type": "text/vnd.tiddlywiki",
        "text": "\\procedure doc-url(url)\r\n<$let topic={{{ [<url>split[.html]last[]] }}}\r\n      ourl= {{{[<topic>addprefix[https://tiddlywiki.com]]}}} >\r\n<a href=<<ourl>> target=_blank><$text text={{{[<topic>removeprefix[#]] :and[decodeuricomponent[]] }}} /></a>\r\n\\end"
